### GET - List All Institutos 
GET {{api}}

### GET - Get Instituto by OK Key
GET {{api}}/3


### GET - Get Instituto by OK Key (explicit)
GET {{api}}/2?keyType=OK


### GET - Get Instituto by BK Key
GET {{api}}/15061?keyType=BK
