###  POST - Create New Instituto
POST {{api}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "IdInstitutoOK": "1001",
  "IdInstitutoBK": "15060",
  "DesInstituto": "Instituto Tecnologico de Celaya",
  "Alias": "ITC",
  "Matriz": "Central",
  "Giro": "Educación"
}

### POST - Create Instituto with Optional Fields
