Content-Type: application/json

{
  "IdInstitutoOK": "100",
  "IdInstitutoBK": "15061",
  "DesInstituto": "Instituto Superior de Formación",
  "Alias": "ISFD",
  "Matriz": "Matriz",
  "Giro": "Formación Profesional",
  "IdInstitutoSupOK": "1001"
}

### PUT - Update Instituto Item
